  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00139', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-07', NULL, 'single_choice', '小劉吃豬血糕（B）時喜歡沾著花生粉（P）一起食用，他每吃1塊豬血糕 都會配上5匙花生粉。下列效用函數何者符合小劉的偏好習慣？', '["U=B1/6×P5/6", "U=5B+P", "U=min{B,5P}", "U=min{5B,P}"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ec91441b2ca1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79ebb3660238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "405", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00140', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-07', NULL, 'single_choice', '若財貨是劣等財，當人們的所得增加時，在其他條件不變下，市場會有何 反應？', '["均衡價格上漲，均衡數量增加", "均衡價格上漲，均衡數量減少", "均衡價格下跌，均衡數量減少", "均衡價格下跌，均衡數量增加"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ec91441b2ca1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79ebb3660238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "405", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-00141', 'disabled-0a2fc18c', 'disabled-0a2fc18c-moex-112-6948958a', 'sub-disabled-0a2fc18c-07', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設 A 國的生產可能曲線是一條直線且 200 萬噸小麥與 100 萬部電腦的 生產組合落在該直線上，則A國生產1噸小麥的機會成本為何？', '["0", "0.5部電腦", "1部電腦", "2部電腦"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ec91441b2ca1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79ebb3660238", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112050", "c": "405", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
